# UK Internal Market Scheme (UKIMS) Authorisation Checker API Technical Interface Specification (TIS)

## Document summary
This document is the technical interface specification (TIS) for the UKIMs Authorisation Checker API. It shows the processes involved in the exchange of messages between Fast Parcel Operators (FPOs) and this UKIMS API during Great Britain and Northern Ireland (GB/XI) customs movements. It provides definitions and formats used 

## Introduction
This API allows Fast Parcel Operators (FPOs), software developers and third party software users to check if the holders of provided EORI Numbers have a valid UKIMS authorisation. The aim is to avoid possible rejections of goods moving through from GB-NI, which could physically stop the B2B parcels. The API is based on REST principles with a single POST method endpoint that returns data in JSON format. It uses standard HTTP error response codes.

